mres()

Description
    string mres(string $var)
    Wrapper function for mysql_real_escape_string(); shortened to mres.
	
Parameters
    var
		Any valid string value.
		
Return Values
    Returns the escaped string, or FALSE on error. 

Examples
	<?php
		...
		//clean strings
		else if (is_string($var)) {
			$var = mres($var);
			if ($quotes) {
				$var = "'". $var ."'";
			}
		}
		...
	?>